:css
  body {
    font-family: Metropolis, sans-serif;
  }

- workshop_title = @workshop.name.presence || @workshop.course

%p
  Hi
  = @workshop.organizer.name
  ,

%p
  Your
  = link_to "#{workshop_title} workshop", CDO.studio_url("/pd/workshop_dashboard/workshops/#{@workshop.id}", CDO.default_scheme)
  on
  = @workshop.sessions.first.formatted_date
  is still open in the dashboard. Please login now to close it.

%p
  Remember, closing your workshop is important as it triggers the participant survey and lets us know the workshop is done.

%p
  Thanks!
